{"tid":300062,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺班海歸撚好可憐？","createTime":"2017-06-27T14:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T05:14:04.000Z","uid":68626,"like":17,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"355c341489b2e08593b721cdaffb21bde62dfa45","tid":300062,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"係香港有書唔讀 去外國讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同做逃兵無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去外國讀書既<br />\n一係好撚廢(dse 10-16分) 又唔想做asso仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係好撚勁(dse 27-40分) 睇唔起local u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後者唔討論了 一陣又成班撚樣衝出黎話咩我mit grad番黎可唔可憐<br />\n主要想講 班10-16分既廢物<br />\n書又唔撚識讀 淨係靠屋企有幾個錢去外國讀書<br />\n番到黎仲好似好撚威咁 我係乜乜u番黎嫁 成日講係外國生活點 人最慘就係食屎仲要話屎香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去外國讀u既 番到黎對住我地本土派根本抬唔起頭<br />\n我地是但一個同外國搞既top up都屌打佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059292fa953d421a7eb0061a8e3c8148f2fb545a","tid":300062,"uid":16281,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33a1f5fe127880e000d261e021dcf781c8376cd9","tid":300062,"uid":68626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後你繼續喺間公屋上網打飛機<br />\n人哋日日逍遙快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsor<br />\n屋企大把"},{"pid":"78b63a25a643bded2513eca6e957e401a521574e","tid":300062,"uid":77158,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"361a66b6026520c0fb437cba2854ce95a9827db1","tid":300062,"uid":6132,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"篇文好似邊度睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337302ee435cdfa563f809775fbb69f514bb4179",